  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 400f (200c).",
    "rinse the grape leaves and blanch them in boiling water for 30 seconds.",
    "soak the grape leaves in ice water to stop the cooking process.",
    "peel and chop the sweet potato into bite-sized pieces.",
    "cut the carrots into bite-sized pieces.",
    "sauté the mushrooms in coconut oil until tender.",
    "stir in soy sauce, ginger, and garlic.",
    "place the grape leaves on a baking sheet and add the sweet potato, carrots, and mushroom mixture.",
    "drizzle the brown rice on top of the mixture.",
    "cover the baking sheet with foil and roast for 20 minutes.",
    "remove the foil and continue roasting for another 10 minutes.",
    "serve warm and enjoy!"
